snippet.title: Terrorist Takedown 3 HD gameplay
snippet.description:
1920*1080, all max, 2XAA, 16XAF, Vsync on, Windows 7 Ultimate 64bit.
60-60FPS (without Fraps)

Link: http://tirexi.hu/2010/08/12/terrorist-takedown-3-hd-gameplay/

Publisher : CITY Interactive
Developer : CITY Interactive

Minimum System Requirements:
Operating System : Microsoft Windows 2000 / Windows XP / Windows Vista
Processor : Intel Pentium IV at 3.0 GHz or equivalent AMD
Video Card : 128 MB VRAM -- nVidia FX 5 Series or better
Memory : 512 MB RAM (XP) / 1 GB RAM (Vista)
Hard Disk : 3 GB of free Hard Drive space
Sound : DirectX compatible sound card
Direct X : 9.0
Controls : Keyboard & Mouse
Installation : DVD-ROM Drive
